headline: Does Luckin Coffee’s New York Debut Signal Room for More Growth in 2025?
summary: If you have been watching Luckin Coffee’s wild ride on the stock market, you know this is not a stock for the timid. Maybe you are weighing whether to grab a slice of the action or just sit back and watch the show. The company’s shares have delivered returns that are nothing short of jaw-dropping, with an increase of 1,023.6% over the last five years and soaring 130.8% over three years. Even this year, Luckin is up an impressive 41.5%. Sure, the stock cooled off a bit in the past week,...
